{
  "stem": "15197.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at that time, they were also instrumental contacting some people who have trucks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the people who had the trucks didn't know for what they are really going-- what kind of job and what kind of tasks they are going to-- to do.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they were hired as smugglers and they understood this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were brought to the place where Kashak knew that the group is going to wait.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Kashak Rotheiser with the two people, of course, under a gun because they got frightened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They opened-- the opening from the sewers and over 60 people of ghetto fighters came out terrible disheveled.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And on the truck, one was in a German uniform staying on guard on the truck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The other were hidden under blankets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they went out from this street to a small place under-- not far from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The other group, which remained and was waiting for the other truck, was not able to get out anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Germans came and it was a shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one of mine co-workers was, at that time, also killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was the only, really, group at that particular time after-- it was not after the Uprising, but at the end of the Uprising, which was able to get out from the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In the woods, they were not able to be too long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The surrounding Polish population, if they will discover who they are, they will give them out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was much more difficult to hide and to find a hiding place in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because the Germans-- they had special orders that those who were hiding Jews-- they will be killed, as well as the Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the whole house will be killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
